I have both python2.7 and python3.2 installed in Ubuntu 16.04

$ sudo apt-get install python3-setuptools

$ sudo easy_install3 pip
$ sudo pip-3.2 install numpy
$ sudo easy_install3 pip
$ sudo pip-3.5 install numpy
        or
$ sudo pip3.5 install numpy
